            <title>[CAMEL-1001] ExceptionType handledPolicy is not exposed in the XSD</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-1001</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ExceptionType handledPolicy is not exposed in the XSD. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;See nabble thread &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nabble.com/RE%3A-How-to-express-new-%22handled%22-predicate-in-Spring-DSL-p20069223.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://www.nabble.com/RE%3A-How-to-express-new-%22handled%22-predicate-in-Spring-DSL-p20069223.html&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
